    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/2c9407f12395dfe3deb67e644e109cc1.webp?t=1769529457\" width=295 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款身临其境的精密3D平台游戏，背景是一档致命的游戏秀，由精英们主办，供他们扭曲的娱乐活动。自愿报名的参赛者将被运送到一个850米高的垂直塔上，这个塔深埋在地下一个未知的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/d9c96f12b2bea2f4aea0ff9bf3ec9466.poster.avif?t=1769529457\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/d9c96f12b2bea2f4aea0ff9bf3ec9466.webm?t=1769529457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/d9c96f12b2bea2f4aea0ff9bf3ec9466.mp4?t=1769529457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/408940b77a56bf494628871fb3075551.webp?t=1769529457\" width=458 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>困难模式</strong> - 无检查点，并有速通计时器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>休闲模式</strong> - 频繁的检查点，无计时器</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/871491dbd53717cb07975edc3a5e181d.avif?t=1769529457\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras_big/871491dbd53717cb07975edc3a5e181d.avif?t=1769529457 width=800 height=527 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/7574c3a90a2eff08fcdd63881edc4a3f.webp?t=1769529457\" width=285 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >登上塔顶，即可赢取一笔改变人生的巨款和自由。然而，游戏的风险和塔的高度相当——掉下去就完了。每一次跳跃和机动都关乎生死。您能在伊卡洛斯塔中生存下来并逃出生天吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/ef0055c3ca4d902c5528f7fd630b185b.poster.avif?t=1769529457\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/ef0055c3ca4d902c5528f7fd630b185b.webm?t=1769529457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/ef0055c3ca4d902c5528f7fd630b185b.mp4?t=1769529457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167280/extras/0ce2459e41a35433bb69eabc666987bd.webp?t=1769529457\" width=285 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索塔的致命之美，这座巨大的建筑分为四个不同的关卡，每个关卡都有自己独特的美感、新的障碍和更高的难度。</p>",
